Implemented a targeted cue-rule refinement in [spacy_modal_codec.py](/home/barberb/portland-laws.github.io/workspace/codex-work/uscode-modal-hardened-4codex-gpu-8h-20260519T091017Z-codex-compiler_registry/worktrees/agent-codex-compiler_registry-packet-000275-20260519_165700/ipfs_datasets_py/optimizers/logic_theorem_optimizer/spacy_modal_codec.py) to better handle the requested ambiguity pairs (`conditional_normative->temporal`, `frame->conditional_normative`, `frame->temporal`, `temporal->temporal`) in statutory scope conflicts.

What changed:
- Strengthened “strong temporal scope” detection for statutory temporal-token contexts (e.g., temporal scope token + statutory reference) in competing-scope backfill logic ([spacy_modal_codec.py:1907](/home/barberb/portland-laws.github.io/workspace/codex-work/uscode-modal-hardened-4codex-gpu-8h-20260519T091017Z-codex-compiler_registry/worktrees/agent-codex-compiler_registry-packet-000275-20260519_165700/ipfs_datasets_py/optimizers/logic_theorem_optimizer/spacy_modal_codec.py:1907)).
- Expanded conditional-dominant → temporal backfill so temporal support is injected earlier and more strongly under statutory/strong temporal evidence ([spacy_modal_codec.py:2095](/home/barberb/portland-laws.github.io/workspace/codex-work/uscode-modal-hardened-4codex-gpu-8h-20260519T091017Z-codex-compiler_registry/worktrees/agent-codex-compiler_registry-packet-000275-20260519_165700/ipfs_datasets_py/optimizers/logic_theorem_optimizer/spacy_modal_codec.py:2095)).
- Added a secondary statutory conditional→temporal backfill path for low-temporal, nonzero-conditional cases with strong temporal scope ([spacy_modal_codec.py:2125](/home/barberb/portland-laws.github.io/workspace/codex-work/uscode-modal-hardened-4codex-gpu-8h-20260519T091017Z-codex-compiler_registry/worktrees/agent-codex-compiler_registry-packet-000275-20260519_165700/ipfs_datasets_py/optimizers/logic_theorem_optimizer/spacy_modal_codec.py:2125)).
- Strengthened frame-dominant → conditional backfill in strong conditional-scope contexts ([spacy_modal_codec.py:2408](/home/barberb/portland-laws.github.io/workspace/codex-work/uscode-modal-hardened-4codex-gpu-8h-20260519T091017Z-codex-compiler_registry/worktrees/agent-codex-compiler_registry-packet-000275-20260519_165700/ipfs_datasets_py/optimizers/logic_theorem_optimizer/spacy_modal_codec.py:2408)).
- Increased conditional and temporal logit boosts in statutory frame contexts when scope evidence is explicit/strong ([spacy_modal_codec.py:2715](/home/barberb/portland-laws.github.io/workspace/codex-work/uscode-modal-hardened-4codex-gpu-8h-20260519T091017Z-codex-compiler_registry/worktrees/agent-codex-compiler_registry-packet-000275-20260519_165700/ipfs_datasets_py/optimizers/logic_theorem_optimizer/spacy_modal_codec.py:2715), [spacy_modal_codec.py:2757](/home/barberb/portland-laws.github.io/workspace/codex-work/uscode-modal-hardened-4codex-gpu-8h-20260519T091017Z-codex-compiler_registry/worktrees/agent-codex-compiler_registry-packet-000275-20260519_165700/ipfs_datasets_py/optimizers/logic_theorem_optimizer/spacy_modal_codec.py:2757)).

